# Mitra Revamp Dashboard Backend

FastAPI backend untuk dashboard superadmin Mitranesia.

## Jalankan

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
cp .env.example .env
alembic upgrade head
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## Test

```bash
pytest
```
